## **VI. MARKET INTELLIGENCE APPLICATION**

### **🎯 Mission Examples**
* "What's the market sentiment on AI hardware startups and who are the key unpublished players?"
* "Analyze the competitive landscape for quantum computing investment opportunities"
* "Identify emerging trends in sustainable energy from private company announcements"

### **💣 Strategic Reconnaissance Agent**
```javascript
class BroadSpectrumResearchAgent extends BaseAgent {
    constructor(tavilyApiKey) {
        super({
            id: 'broad_spectrum_research',
            name: 'Strategic Reconnaissance Agent',
            capabilities: ['web_research', 'source_synthesis', 'intelligence_briefing']
        });

        this.tavilyClient = new TavilyClient({ apiKey: tavilyApiKey });
    }

    async gatherIntelligence(query, options = {}) {
        const { maxSources = 20, timeRange = 'week', includeImages = false } = options;

        // Broad-spectrum research across multiple sources
        const research = await this.tavilyClient.search({
            query: query,
            max_results: maxSources,
            include_images: includeImages,
            include_answer: true,
            include_raw_content: true
        });

        // Synthesize into intelligence brief
        const intelligence = await this.synthesizeBrief(query, research.results);

        return {
            query: query,
            intelligence: intelligence,
            sources: research.results.map(r => ({ url: r.url, title: r.title })),
            metadata: {
                totalSources: research.results.length,
                searchTime: research.response_time,
                confidence: this.calculateConfidence(research.results)
            }
        };
    }
}
```

### **🎯 Surgical Strike Agent**
```javascript
class TargetedExtractionAgent extends BaseAgent {
    constructor(brightDataApiKey) {
        super({
            id: 'targeted_extraction',
            name: 'Surgical Strike Agent',
            capabilities: ['targeted_extraction', 'proxy_handling', 'captcha_solving']
        });

        this.brightDataClient = new BrightDataClient({ apiKey: brightDataApiKey });
    }

    async extractTarget(url, options = {}) {
        const { useProxy = true, solveCaptcha = true, waitForElements = [] } = options;

        // Surgical strike on protected target
        const extraction = await this.brightDataClient.scrape({
            url: url,
            use_proxy: useProxy,
            solve_captcha: solveCaptcha,
            wait_for_elements: waitForElements,
            return_html: false, // We want structured data
            return_text: true
        });

        // Process and clean the extracted data
        const processedData = await this.processExtractedData(extraction);

        return {
            url: url,
            extractedData: processedData,
            metadata: {
                extractionTime: extraction.response_time,
                proxyUsed: extraction.proxy_used,
                captchaSolved: extraction.captcha_solved
            }
        };
    }
}
```

### **🧠 Zeta Brain Agent**
```javascript
class SynthesisAnalysisAgent extends BaseAgent {
    constructor(model = 'gpt-4o') {
        super({
            id: 'zeta_brain',
            name: 'Zeta Intelligence Brain',
            capabilities: ['data_synthesis', 'pattern_analysis', 'report_generation']
        });

        this.llm = new LLMClient({ model: model });
    }

    async synthesizeIntelligence(reconData, extractionData, query) {
        // Cross-reference all intelligence
        const crossReferenced = await this.crossReferenceData(reconData, extractionData);

        // Identify patterns and contradictions
        const patterns = await this.identifyPatterns(crossReferenced);
        const contradictions = await this.findContradictions(crossReferenced);

        // Generate final intelligence report
        const report = await this.generateIntelligenceReport({
            query: query,
            crossReferencedData: crossReferenced,
            patterns: patterns,
            contradictions: contradictions,
            confidence: this.calculateOverallConfidence(crossReferenced)
        });

        return report;
    }
}
```

### **🎯 Zeta Orchestrator**
```javascript
class ZetaOrchestrator extends BaseAgent {
    constructor() {
        super({
            id: 'zeta_orchestrator',
            name: 'Zeta Mission Commander',
            capabilities: ['mission_planning', 'agent_coordination', 'intelligence_routing']
        });

        this.reconAgent = new BroadSpectrumResearchAgent(process.env.TAVILY_API_KEY);
        this.sniperAgent = new TargetedExtractionAgent(process.env.BRIGHTDATA_API_KEY);
        this.brainAgent = new SynthesisAnalysisAgent();
    }

    async executeIntelligenceMission(query) {
        try {
            // Phase 1: Strategic Reconnaissance
            logger.info('💣 Starting Strategic Reconnaissance...');
            const reconResults = await this.reconAgent.gatherIntelligence(query);

            // Phase 2: Identify High-Value Targets
            const highValueTargets = await this.identifyHighValueTargets(reconResults);

            // Phase 3: Surgical Strikes (if needed)
            let extractionResults = [];
            if (highValueTargets.length > 0) {
                logger.info('🎯 Executing Surgical Strikes...');
                extractionResults = await this.executeSurgicalStrikes(highValueTargets);
            }

            // Phase 4: Final Synthesis
            logger.info('🧠 Synthesizing Intelligence...');
            const finalReport = await this.brainAgent.synthesizeIntelligence(
                reconResults,
                extractionResults,
                query
            );

            return finalReport;

        } catch (error) {
            logger.error('Intelligence mission failed:', error);
            throw error;
        }
    }
}
```

